{"tid":1400182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"K11 同旺角有伏 向紅磡土瓜灣走","createTime":"2019-08-03T11:37:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T13:32:41.000Z","uid":113953,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ca74e5aaceb167e3c98296426b2568c0d8af90bc","tid":1400182,"uid":113953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:37:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mJpDX6h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmJpDX6h.png&h=22eb9b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">K11 同旺角都係伏</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n狗隻想由尖東西九將人由尖沙咀推入旺角圍死<br />\n<br />\n旺角 - 一早已經落閘，女人街都冇開，明顯係伏，仲要大敗過<br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀 - cut地鐵同渡輪就直接玩完<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n28號上環嘅歷史係<br />\n<br />\n狗車守山，重兵西環，再係灣仔快速向西推進，前線除咗跳海就只能被圍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日玩法一模一樣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要守？水炮車直接爆防線<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">向紅磡方向散開，至少離開陷阱。</span></span>"},{"pid":"868d4514acdbeb99bf7c78a71b6e22a27e639503","tid":1400182,"uid":92426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd7474544598e14689742795b940e56a3e8ad4a","tid":1400182,"uid":263103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"Be water"},{"pid":"df7964d1442a7717e5f0a752d39cab5a50ec2b62","tid":1400182,"uid":46848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:47:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c60a86679b434d677ed3f66203355c021926b70a","tid":1400182,"uid":46848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:57:10.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"6d25b2a448fc014675789347496ca83d543542d0","tid":1400182,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca74e5aaceb167e3c98296426b2568c0d8af90bc"